            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/683.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/683.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut the <strong>fish</strong> fillets in half widthways</p>\r\n<p>Tap a few tbsp of <strong>flour</strong> out onto a plate, then beat the <strong>egg<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> and pour them into a shallow bowl</p>\r\n<p>Pour the panko <strong>breadcrumbs</strong> onto a third plate, then coat the fish in <strong>flour</strong>, then <strong>egg</strong> and finally <strong>breadcrumbs</strong>, pressing firmly to coat them evenly and set aside&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/683.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/683.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/683.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/683.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/683.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the<strong> brioche</strong> buns in half</p>\r\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based dry pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the buns, cut-side down, and toast them for 3 min or until coloured and charred on one side only</p>\r\n<p>Once charred, remove and set aside until serving and reserve the pan</p>",
